                .accept(MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON)
                .contentType(MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON)
                .retrieve()
                .bodyToMono(String.class)
                .retry(RETRY_COUNT);
    }


Your `searchResource()` method would be called when `getServerCredential(resourceType)` emitted the value.

